{{message|You stiffen momentarily.|Free action prevented a potion of paralysis or its vapors from paralyzing you.}}
{{message|You momentarily stiffen under <monster>'s gaze!|Free action prevented a floating eye's passive gaze from paralyzing you.<ref name="hiteye"/>}}
{{message|You stiffen momentarily under <monster>'s gaze.|As above, while you are polymorphed into a monster with a gaze attack that you used on the floating eye.<ref name="polyeye"/>}}
